Package: rein
Type: Package
Title: Distribution Grid Reinforcement Optimization
Version: 2.0.1
Date: 2018-01-29
Authors@R: c(person("Wolfgang", "Biener", email = "wolfgang.biener@ise.fraunhofer.de", role = c("aut", "cre")), person("Andre", "Siono", email = "andre.siono@ise.fraunhofer.de", role = c("aut")))
Description: The package takes a grid data and calculates the optimum reinforcement measures. Reinforcement measures are categorized into three main methods: conventional, OLTC and Reactive Power Control(RPC). Grid data and load should be in list format specifying its busses, asset types, and loads. 
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
